item.title: About me
item.description: Maciej (Matthew) Morycinski retired from being an industrial automation technologist, to pursue creative interests and hobbies. Born in Poland, he now lives in Canada, in the province of British Columbia, city of Burnaby. His blog aims to entertain, educate, maybe provoke reflection. You can e-mail him at: m at tt dot moryce dot ca Your critical remarks are welcome as much as praise. Thanks for reading!
